            water supply valve to stop more water from entering the tank and
            exacerbating the leak. Assess the source of the leak; it could be
            from the pressure relief valve, connections, or due to a corroded
            tank. Contact a professional plumber to evaluate the extent of the
            damage and determine whether a repair or full replacement is
            necessary.
